379
00:48:13,393 --> 00:48:15,771
- Kredom krug i stajati u njemu.
- Krug.

380
00:48:16,021 --> 00:48:18,857
- Eto tako.
- I stajati.

381
00:48:19,650 --> 00:48:23,153
Ona nece moci da prodje.

382
00:48:25,030 --> 00:48:28,700
To je sveti krug. Nece proci. Da.

383
00:48:29,284 --> 00:48:30,827
Da, razumeo sam.

384
00:48:31,828 --> 00:48:35,165
- Kredom krug i stoj.
- Samo moras da se molis.

385
00:48:35,415 --> 00:48:37,543
Razumeo sam, treba mi krug.

386
00:48:38,794 --> 00:48:41,630
- Potreban je krug.
- Tri nocne mise ...

387
00:48:42,089 --> 00:48:46,552
...to je obred sahrane vestice.

388
00:48:46,885 --> 00:48:50,722
Ako te pobedi, vaskrsnuce.

389
00:48:55,727 --> 00:48:59,857
Pratili smo put. Isao je
od napustene farme.

390
00:49:00,190 --> 00:49:03,193
